text: Adriano Morais (born 21 February 1948) is a Portuguese wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Portugal Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Torres Vedras
